VK Aromatics to Open Serbian Plant Next Month, Novosti Reports

-- B y   M i s h a   S a v i c
-- 
2011-05-25T08:03:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-25/vk-aromatics-to-open-serbian-plant-next-month-novosti-reports.html
VK Aromatics  will open a plant in
 Serbia  next month and start producing aromatic additives for
food and beverages,  Vecernje Novosti  newspaper reported, citing
owner Victor Koh and Miroslav Delic, his Serbian venture
partner.  VK Aromatics, based in  Singapore , aims to sell these
additives in south-eastern  Europe  and  Russia , the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Misha Savic in Belgrade at 
 msavic2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  